snippet.title: Best VGM 1606 - Tales of Vesperia - The Tormenting Whisper of Water
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1065 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gSLIlAVZ6Eo
Best VGM 2179 - https://youtu.be/MaiHaXRYtNQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3
Tales of Vesperia (2008)
The Tormenting Whisper of Water
Motoi Sakuraba
